//circle.hydla
//bouncing particle in a circle

INIT   <=> x = 0 /\ 99/100 = y /\ x' = 2 /\ y' = 1.
RUN    <=> [](x'' = 0 /\ y'' = -5).
BOUNCE <=> []((x-)^2 + (y-)^2 = 1 => 
                x' = x'- - (x- * x'- + y- * y'-) * 2 * (x-) /\
                y' = y'- - (x- * x'- + y- * y'-) * 2 * (y-)
).
INIT, RUN<<BOUNCE.